#### About Me
Rabe Abdalkareem is a Ph.D. student at [Concordia University](https://www.concordia.ca/) supervised by [Dr. Juergen Rilling](https://sites.google.com/site/juergenrilling/)â€Ž and [Dr. Emad Shihab](http://users.encs.concordia.ca/~eshihab/index.html). He received his MSc. in Computer Science and Software Engineering from  Concordia university. His research interests include software engineering, software evolution and maintenance, mining software repositories, software reuse, machine learning and applications of Semantic Web in software engineering.
